snippet.title: Slendrina Must Die: The Cellar
snippet.description:
Game is now LIVE on FaceBook https://www.facebook.com/games/smdthecellar/?fbs=106

Android Download Link - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.SMDC

PC Download link: http://gamejolt.com/games/slendrina-must-die-the-cellar/167474

After you searched the house and found all
8 pieces of painting, Slenderman knock you out.
You know the secret of Slendrina, and
now you can't leave the house.

They throw you in their cellar.
This place looks more like The Bunker.
You must find 8 books if you want to
leave this place alive! Good Luck!

* Four weapons: 
- Knife
- Gun
- Shotgun
- MP5

* Awesome 3D Graphics

Game is based on Slendrina:The Cellar
